Generation Modes: Supports two modes,Image-to-3D and Multi-view-to-3D;

Generation Types: Supports three types, All-in-One Generation (geometry + textures), Staged Generation (geometry first, then textures), and Geometry-only.;

Model Versions: Supports calling v1.0 and v1.5 versions of general models, as well as specialized models for portrait scenarios;

Model Resolutions: Supports four resolutions: 512³, 1024³, 1536³, and 1536³ Pro;

Model Formats: Supports output of four model formats: .obj, .glb, .stl, .fbx.


